LogData.text: After all these months we have finally something to show for our hard work. It didn’t even make a drop of the stuff and took a lot of resources and energy, but it’s a start that we can improve on. Our focus now is to optimize our method to the point that it becomes profitable. Right now we’d have to spend weeks to get even enough for a few pills. There’s a lot more work to be done but we finally got a foothold.
